6/ Our design co-founder will be joining @DropboxDesign and will continue to apply her Memo knowledge as part of the @Dropbox Paper team.

4/ We think this is an important problem but we didn’t succeed in finding product/market fit and building a sustainable business. While we know this is a sad day, we’re super optimistic about what’s next. If you have questions or concerns, please contact us at team@memo.ai
